keel.Algorithms.Genetic_Rule_Learning.XCS

Interface Attribute

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    IntegerRep, RealRep, TernaryRep

    public interface Attribute

    This interface has to be implemented for all attributes representation. By now, there are 3 implementations. Each one is a diferent attribute representation: - Real Representation - Integer Representation - Ternary Representation

    Since:
    JDK1.2

    Version:
    1.1
    Author:
    Written by Albert Orriols (La Salle, Ramón Llull University - Barcelona) 28/03/2004, Modified by Xavi Solé (La Salle, Ramón Llull University - Barcelona) 03/12/2008
